SIMPLE: repeal
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Repeal
<hw>Re*peal"</hw> <pr>(r?-p?l")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Repealed</conjf>
<pr>(-p?ld")</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Repealing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[OF. <ets>repeler</ets> to call
back, F. <ets>rappeler</ets>; pref. <ets>re-</ets> re- + OF.
<ets>apeler</ets>, F. <ets>appeler</ets>, to call, L.
<ets>appellare</ets>. See <er>Appeal</er>, and. cf.
<er>Repel</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To recall; to summon again, as
persons.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The banished Bolingbroke <qex>repeals</qex> himself,⟦br⟧
And with uplifted arms is safe arrived.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To recall, as a deed, will, law, or statute; to
revoke; to rescind or abrogate by authority, as by act of the
legislature; <as>as, to <ex>repeal</ex> a law</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>To suppress; to repel.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whence Adam soon <qex>repealed</qex>⟦br⟧
The doubts that in his heart arose.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- To abolish; revoke; rescind; recall; annul;
abrogate; cancel; reverse. See <er>Abolish</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Repeal</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Repeal
<hw>Re*peal"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Recall, as from
exile.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The tribunes are no soldiers; and their people⟦br⟧
Will be as rash in the <qex>repeal</qex>, as hasty⟦br⟧
To expel him thence.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Revocation; abrogation; <as>as, the <ex>repeal</ex>
of a statute; the <ex>repeal</ex> of a law or a usage.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Repealability</ent>⟦br⟧
